## Planning Document: SIMD Expansion Roadmap

### New Section Added

**PLAN_TO_PORT_SCRIPTBOTS_TO_MODERN_IDIOMATIC_RUST_USING_GPUI.md** (lines 172-264):

Added comprehensive 92-line section titled **"SIMD Expansion Targets and Implementation Details [Planned]"** enumerating 10 concrete optimization opportunities beyond the already-shipped Phase 1 work.

### Subsections

1. **Eyes: precompute trigonometry and use dot-product angular tests** [Planned]
