   - Precompute per-agent per-eye unit vectors once per tick
   - Vectorize 4 eyes with `wide::f32x4`
   - Target: ≥2-4% win at 2k/1k ticks

2. **Blood cone: lane-wise forward cone via dot threshold** [Planned]
