   - Target: ≥1-2% win at 5k/1k ticks

6. **Actuation: heading/velocity/energy drain in 4-agent blocks** [Planned]
   - Homogeneous actuation math batched across agents
   - Integrate terrain gradient dot heading (item 9)
   - Target: ≥2-3% win at 5k/1k ticks

7. **Food regrowth: decay/growth/diffusion in 4-wide strides** [Planned]
   - Row-wise neighbor averaging in 4-wide SIMD packs
   - Handle edges with scalar tail
   - Target: ≥10-15% speedup of regrowth stage; ≥1-2% overall

8. **Carcass distribution: neighbor distance tests and shares** [Planned]
   - SIMD distance masks and per-lane shares
   - Maintain neighbor ordering for determinism
   - Target: ≥1% overall win at 5k/1k ticks

9. **Terrain gradients in locomotion: gradient dot heading** [Planned]
   - Batch slope penalty/gain via SIMD dot products
   - Apply when topography enabled
   - Target: Measurable improvement with no regressions

10. **UniformGridIndex neighbor SoA iterator** [Planned]
    - Add API returning contiguous `x[]`, `y[]` slices instead of AoS
    - Reduce gathers; improve SIMD load efficiency
    - Target: ≥1-2% win in sensing/combat at 5k+ agents

